CreateC++Project for Windows

A simple tool to create C++ project structure on Windows.

Using Compiler for Windows: MinGW

Usage:
1. Copy CreateC++Project.exe to a folder in your PATH (e.g. C:\Windows or add custom folder to PATH)
2. Open Command Prompt (CMD) or Terminal
3. Run:

    CreateC++Project

This will generate a basic C++ project with source files and build setup.

Author: Devdez